'''Ariadne Crater''' is a [[List of craters on Venus|crater]] on [[Venus]]. Its central peak serves as the [[prime meridian]] of the planet, a status formerly held by [[Eve (crater)|Eve Crater]] until relocated.<ref>[http://www2.jpl.nasa.gov/magellan/guide8.html JPL "What's in a Name"]</ref>

