{{No footnotes|article|date=March 2011}}
In [[graphonomics]], '''Axial pen force''' is the [[vector (geometric)|component]] of the [[normal pen force]] that is parallel to the pen. It is dependent upon [[pen tilt]]. In the special case of a perfectly vertical orientation of the [[writing instrument]] the axial pen force
equals the [[normal pen force]].

